WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.394 --> 00:00:01.217
Good morning, family!

00:00:01.217 --> 00:00:02.305
How are you all doing?

00:00:02.570 --> 00:00:06.663
It's evening here now, but I always say good morning because it's morning somewhere.

00:00:07.885 --> 00:00:19.460
I always come here to this campus because of what the Lord has shown me, and these praying hands when I drive by mean so much to me.

00:00:20.060 --> 00:00:23.835
The motto of the school is 'Make no little plans here.

00:00:23.835 --> 00:00:26.934
' This is the ORU campus, by the way.

00:00:27.188 --> 00:00:37.420
I was driving by tonight and the Holy Spirit was stirring in me so strongly about the revival that's about to take place at this campus.

00:00:38.050 --> 00:00:45.780
It's just what faith will build, what faith will do when you use your faith like a muscle.

00:00:47.140 --> 00:00:48.164
It's important, y'all.

00:00:48.164 --> 00:00:53.399
I drive by this because it inspires me to think big.

00:00:54.360 --> 00:00:56.860
This is what Oral Roberts believed God for.

00:00:58.399 --> 00:01:11.771
Every day I try to drive around here at least once to inspire myself.

00:01:11.771 --> 00:01:56.335
The towers over there where the hospital was—I know they've sold that recently—but just the Mabee Center, because the Lord showed me there will be a major outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord in that big coliseum once again.

00:01:56.335 --> 00:02:06.640
The old wells of revival are coming uncapped.

00:02:07.100 --> 00:02:11.206
I come and I look at the Prayer Tower—can you see the Prayer Tower right there?

00:02:11.206 --> 00:03:18.070
That's where they pray, and I just thought it's exciting because some of the greatest ministers of any generation—I mean, from Kathryn Kuhlman to Benny Hinn to all the greats that have come through here and had healing services and deliverance services—look at what God did at one point through this right here and what an amazing thing he's going to do again.

00:03:20.415 --> 00:03:26.760
I showed you Victory, and I'm just excited because expectation brings manifestation.

00:03:31.208 --> 00:04:18.839
It has nothing to do with me; it's just something that I pray over because I know that God is going to visit the young generation again with one last call, one last harvest, a major harvest of souls like we've never seen before.

00:04:26.524 --> 00:04:26.848
The glory of the Lord with fire...

00:04:39.404 --> 00:05:00.768
I believe that there will be signs and wonders in the last days like with Azusa Street when there was a pillar of fire shown over Azusa Street.

00:05:00.768 --> 00:05:48.220
I'm believing there will be a pillar of fire over this Mabee Center and a pillar of fire over this ORU campus, and that there will be a greater revival than even what happened at Asbury.

00:06:03.170 --> 00:06:39.091
That revival kind of fizzled out, but my goodness, I know that we're on the cusp of something huge about to take place in this Tulsa metroplex area and that God is about to do something huge in these last days.

00:06:39.091 --> 00:07:03.320
Diana is with me now, and we made it where the green screen would be at the hands.

00:07:03.320 --> 00:07:20.212
It was so cold I had to get out of being outside.

00:07:23.417 --> 00:07:42.897
I told her I can't make this video at the campus; I was freezing, the wind was blowing so hard, and it was cold.

00:07:42.897 --> 00:07:50.950
I told Brandon, 'Are you cold?

00:07:50.950 --> 00:08:03.520
' and he goes, 'Yeah,' so we left.

00:08:03.520 --> 00:08:07.444
We have such an urgency as we make the rest of this video for you.

00:08:08.333 --> 00:08:24.960
The things the Lord has been putting on our hearts—He said, 'Brandon, people are not awake yet.

00:08:24.960 --> 00:08:37.985
There's no sense of urgency even in the upper leadership.

00:08:37.985 --> 00:09:03.106
' They have a form of urgency, but deep down in their hearts, there's not a stirring.

00:09:03.106 --> 00:09:14.400
People say, 'Well, you're judging people.

00:09:14.400 --> 00:09:31.783
' No, I'm not judging people; I'm just saying what He says.

00:09:31.783 --> 00:09:55.379
I have no idea what you feel, but I know what the Holy Spirit has told me.

00:09:55.379 --> 00:10:08.451
If you don't agree with it, take it up with Him.

00:10:17.644 --> 00:10:23.579
All I can say is what He's told me and what we pray about.

00:10:33.074 --> 00:10:51.733
The Lord said, 'I'm going to bring a greater shaking to awaken beyond anybody's comprehension of what's about to happen.

00:10:51.733 --> 00:11:00.910
' Folks, I'm telling you, a major shaking.

00:11:00.910 --> 00:11:10.977
People say that sounds like fear.

00:11:10.977 --> 00:11:39.999
Diana and I were talking about how people say we are fear-mongers, or that our channel has grown because we preach fear and fear sells.

00:11:50.599 --> 00:11:52.199
But folks, it's not fear; it's an awakening unto God.

00:11:52.199 --> 00:12:09.985
If you're in fear, it's because you're not awake.

00:12:09.985 --> 00:12:44.015
Your heart should be looking vertical with Him, and that shouldn't scare you when He says these things are going to happen because we're dead to self.

00:12:45.946 --> 00:12:58.786
We are looking for the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:12:58.786 --> 00:13:03.960
He told me, 'Brandon, there's no urgency in my body.

00:13:03.960 --> 00:13:19.031
' Do you really realize He is on His way?

00:13:23.573 --> 00:13:53.279
Do you really realize that this is the last call for the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen?

00:13:53.279 --> 00:14:11.360
As we sit on the ORU campus with these hands behind us, they mean something: prayer changes things.

00:14:11.360 --> 00:14:25.579
Somebody used their faith to get those hands there.

00:14:25.579 --> 00:15:07.611
That campus and the Mabee Center cost millions of dollars; it was Oral Roberts' faith that brought that forth, using his faith as a tool to build the university for God.

00:15:19.966 --> 00:15:30.584
He gave all the glory to God, taking healing to the nations and raising up doctors.

00:15:30.584 --> 00:15:45.506
But the Lord said, 'Brandon, there's one more wave.

00:15:45.506 --> 00:16:13.514
' Those old wells that had been capped, the Lord said, 'I capped them, and I'm uncapping those wells.

00:16:13.514 --> 00:17:05.520
' As you saw that church, Victory, He said Victory and ORU will be an extension of each other in the days ahead, and you will see a major outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord greater than even Asbury.

00:17:05.520 --> 00:17:22.600
That was nothing compared to what's about to happen with that Mabee Center and all throughout Tulsa.

00:17:22.600 --> 00:18:06.800
Victory Church across the street holds probably 10,000 in its auditorium—it's a massive one—and then they have the Mabee Center, which is a little over 10,000 seats.

00:18:06.800 --> 00:18:17.966
So you have a 15,000-seat capacity between the two.

00:18:17.966 --> 00:18:27.180
They could do a simulcast and have an overflow.

00:18:42.071 --> 00:18:50.459
It doesn't matter; when the glory is there, it's about a radical move of the Spirit of God one last time.

00:18:50.459 --> 00:18:55.880
Now I see it.

00:18:55.880 --> 00:19:13.400
Do you remember I told you He was going to use the angels?

00:19:13.400 --> 00:19:27.954
He told me, 'Brandon, I'm sending my reserves, my angel army reserves.

00:19:27.954 --> 00:19:53.406
' There's going to be two angels per person, no matter how many demonic spirits there are on the earth.

00:19:53.406 --> 00:19:57.120
Greater is He that is in you than he that is in the world.

00:19:57.120 --> 00:20:11.830
I was listening to Sister Billy talk about old stories and how John G.

00:20:11.830 --> 00:20:33.622
Lake would put a beautiful white suit on every day because he saw himself as a carrier of the glory.

00:20:33.622 --> 00:20:47.720
He saw himself as someone who carried God to the nations.

00:20:47.720 --> 00:20:58.316
There were over 100,000 documented miracles through his ministry.

00:21:10.150 --> 00:21:10.505
He got radically on fire going to Azusa.

00:21:10.505 --> 00:21:34.141
There is a cross-pollination with the glory; as you are on fire, you light somebody else on fire.

00:21:34.141 --> 00:21:50.440
It's not just about the churches, folks, but God told me specifically that He was going to do something huge on the ORU campus, that there would be a major healing revival coming forth with the young people there.

00:21:53.954 --> 00:22:03.660
That's why I go and pray and drive around Lewis Avenue, just praying in the Spirit.

00:22:03.660 --> 00:22:10.653
I'm hungry, I'm desperate, and I want change.

00:22:10.653 --> 00:22:27.393
I am so tired of having church that's just normal.

00:22:33.555 --> 00:22:47.400
The Lord said, 'There's no urgency in my churches, for the coming of my Son is at hand.

00:22:47.400 --> 00:23:12.890
' Many believe it's far off, but I'm trying to tell you, just like Paul Revere riding in the midnight hour, that Jesus is coming.

00:23:12.890 --> 00:23:23.764
He's shaking me to awaken me every day.

00:23:37.479 --> 00:23:37.786
I wake up with an urgency to tell you there's a storm coming.

00:23:37.786 --> 00:23:56.750
I'm here to tell you there's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

00:23:56.750 --> 00:24:11.426
I'm trying to shake you until your teeth rattle: Jesus is coming!

00:24:11.426 --> 00:24:58.103
When I went to the Tribulation with Him and He took me out of my body, Jesus told me there would be one major push, a major revival that does not last that long—a glorious church that will rise up like Tommy Hicks' vision.

00:25:01.103 --> 00:25:03.849
You can Google 'Tommy Hicks vision.

00:25:03.849 --> 00:25:11.530
' The body will move like a mighty giant.

00:25:11.530 --> 00:25:35.570
The Lord said to me, 'Brandon, it's not about the charismatics or non-denominational; I'm going to pour out my Spirit upon all flesh.

00:25:35.570 --> 00:25:46.273
' It's going to be a denominational barrier-buster.

00:25:56.320 --> 00:25:56.650
The Lord is bringing these walls down.

00:25:56.650 --> 00:26:05.046
We will move as a body.

00:26:08.040 --> 00:26:29.514
In World War II, the men were at war and the women helped in the factories to support them.

00:26:29.514 --> 00:26:38.159
In the body of Christ, we're a family.

00:26:38.159 --> 00:26:57.057
It's about taking down religious walls and knowing it's one for all, like the Three Musketeers.

00:27:03.709 --> 00:27:06.114
It's about getting the lost saved.

00:27:06.114 --> 00:27:21.606
We all have the same cause: to reach the lost for Jesus.

00:27:21.606 --> 00:27:32.200
Let's join together regardless of what our beliefs are.

00:27:32.200 --> 00:27:51.360
Does the fact that I believe in the gifts make me better than you?

00:27:51.360 --> 00:27:59.253
No, it just makes me hungry.

00:28:17.100 --> 00:28:17.355
The devil has divided us.

00:28:23.754 --> 00:28:27.868
Just like racial issues—skin shouldn't matter; we're brothers and sisters.

00:28:36.788 --> 00:28:43.955
It's time to put away petty differences and rise up as a body.

00:28:54.500 --> 00:29:03.091
You may be the hand and I might be the foot, but we work together.

00:29:03.091 --> 00:29:14.819
Even the parts that are not seen are sometimes the most vital.

00:29:14.819 --> 00:29:20.040
I have such hunger and anticipation.

00:29:20.040 --> 00:29:35.679
He told me, 'Brandon, I'm going to shake this world like it's never been shaken before.

00:29:35.679 --> 00:29:47.373
' You're about to see earthquakes, volcanoes, and signs in the heavens.

00:29:47.373 --> 00:29:58.080
It's going to shake the ones pretending to be awake.

00:29:58.080 --> 00:30:08.425
He said His remnant doesn't even have an urgency.

00:30:08.425 --> 00:30:31.199
The ones standing in the way will be removed, and He will bring up the ones who are hungry and desperate.

00:30:45.809 --> 00:30:52.959
The ones with a religious nose to the sky will either go to the graveside or be removed.

00:30:52.959 --> 00:31:00.175
He's looking for a yielded 'yes.

00:31:00.175 --> 00:31:19.880
' We came across this prophecy Sister Billy was talking about from Brother Kenneth E.

00:31:19.880 --> 00:31:20.960
Hagin.

00:31:20.960 --> 00:31:36.679
He gave this word back in 1983, and it goes alongside what I'm telling you.

00:31:36.679 --> 00:31:50.399
Tapping into the Spirit realm will be like taking a breath.

00:31:50.399 --> 00:32:02.614
Holy Ghost rivers are coming like a mighty rushing wind.

00:32:02.614 --> 00:32:17.115
Diana reads much better than me, so I asked her to read this.

00:32:17.115 --> 00:32:20.382
It's from 1983.

00:32:20.382 --> 00:32:39.559
In this move, you have not seen the revival of divine healing that you're about to see.

00:32:39.559 --> 00:33:02.620
You saw those I raised up as a pilot program, but many just lifted them up in pride and the anointing left them.

00:33:02.620 --> 00:33:09.211
Some became money-minded and lost the anointing.

00:33:09.211 --> 00:33:23.873
But there will arise a brand-new breed; they'll not be greedy of filthy lucre.

00:33:23.873 --> 00:33:31.365
They won't want to attract attention to themselves.

00:33:42.969 --> 00:33:49.839
God will use laymen, and there'll be a revival of divine healing such as you have not seen.

00:33:51.239 --> 00:34:10.019
The supernatural will not only be in casting out devils and healing, but in the seen realm.

00:34:10.019 --> 00:34:27.479
Men will see the glory of God; a cloud will hang over congregations for days.

00:34:27.479 --> 00:34:45.449
Sinner and saint alike will wonder what it is.

00:34:45.449 --> 00:34:56.811
There will be the fire of the Spirit in manifestation.

00:34:56.811 --> 00:35:03.680
People will see fire on top of buildings.

00:35:03.909 --> 00:35:17.215
The Lord will use signs of His presence to bring people into full salvation.

00:35:29.066 --> 00:35:38.040
The glory of God will fall, and people will even be transported like Philip was.

00:35:51.040 --> 00:36:02.040
The Lord is the same God today; He can make the iron axe-head float and feed 5,000 with a boy's lunch.

00:36:12.100 --> 00:36:23.747
Many shall be astonished, but the greatest miracle is that so many fish will be caught in the net that the nets can't hold them.

00:36:27.440 --> 00:36:37.474
The Lord said, 'Brandon, it's time to get a bigger net.

00:36:37.474 --> 00:37:02.280
' There won't be church houses enough to hold the people.

00:37:02.280 --> 00:37:26.257
Quit fishing in your bathtub; go out where the fish are and throw out the net.

00:37:26.257 --> 00:37:44.280
Many of you will stand in a place of ministry ordained from the foundation of the earth.

00:37:44.280 --> 00:38:05.640
If it could be told in human vernacular, it would almost blow your mind.

00:38:05.640 --> 00:38:25.480
That was in 1983, so it's not a little ways off anymore; we're there.

00:38:25.813 --> 00:38:35.880
The manifestation of the Spirit shall be to full potential.

00:38:35.880 --> 00:38:53.395
Let me give you further wise advice: don't try to do it yourself.

00:39:05.656 --> 00:39:06.048
Just learn to relax and flow with the Spirit.

00:39:06.048 --> 00:39:46.280
You'll not come into the full potential tomorrow or next week, but as you're faithful and learn to yield, you'll move into that place.

00:39:46.280 --> 00:40:13.729
Moving into that place is fueled by prayer, fired by the Spirit, and ignited with His glory.

00:40:13.729 --> 00:40:24.370
If there's no fuel, there's nothing to fire.

00:40:28.855 --> 00:40:44.546
It's like a furnace; the pilot light fires it, and then the whole thing becomes ignited.

00:40:44.546 --> 00:40:49.640
It's the prayer.

00:40:49.640 --> 00:41:16.693
That's what brought Azusa; they were in that little house praying and then the earthquake happened.

00:41:24.400 --> 00:41:30.480
This is part two of the prophetic word.

00:41:30.480 --> 00:41:46.893
I feel it's important to keep going over these nuggets from the archives.

00:41:46.893 --> 00:42:01.280
They were given 40 years ago, and it's time for them to manifest.

00:42:02.137 --> 00:42:15.244
You're on the verge of the greatest move this world has ever seen.

00:42:15.244 --> 00:42:55.302
If you give more earnest heed to what you've heard about the Holy Spirit and angels, for Joel prophesied that in the last days God would pour out His Spirit upon all flesh.

00:42:55.302 --> 00:43:02.936
Young men and women will prophesy.

00:43:08.440 --> 00:43:16.590
The work God intended shall be accomplished, and things must be speeded up.

00:43:16.590 --> 00:43:25.305
You'll learn faster and mature overnight.

00:43:25.305 --> 00:43:43.725
Some who have let these things slip shall be restored tonight.

00:43:51.985 --> 00:43:55.085
The glory of God shall rest upon thee.

00:43:56.520 --> 00:44:11.320
It will seem as though the building is filled with smoke.

00:44:22.186 --> 00:44:27.854
The noise of praise and adoration shall be noised abroad.

00:44:32.410 --> 00:45:05.720
The Lord shall be a manifestation in all ways He has ever manifested, plus the multiplying of His power in these days as men grow more wicked.

00:45:09.376 --> 00:45:17.423
The glory shall flow like a mighty river.

00:45:17.423 --> 00:45:27.594
Millions will be swept into it.

00:45:27.594 --> 00:45:56.104
Men will walk into a place of business and people will fall on their knees because of the glory.

00:46:06.875 --> 00:46:14.585
It will be very difficult for you to believe what shall shortly come to pass.

00:46:14.585 --> 00:46:56.320
But as you walk with the Lord, your heart shall be prepared until you flow into the supernatural as naturally as a bird flies through the air or a fish swims in the water.

00:46:56.320 --> 00:47:11.599
You'll flow in the supernatural as naturally as you breathe the air.

00:47:11.599 --> 00:47:32.600
You'll not be conscious of your faith, but rather the flow of the Spirit.

00:47:33.140 --> 00:47:55.583
The Lord told me walking in the supernatural will be like taking a breath; it will be effortless.

00:47:55.583 --> 00:48:11.847
Brother Hagin said it in 1983 when I was in diapers.

00:48:21.427 --> 00:48:21.889
God doesn't change His mind.

00:48:21.889 --> 00:48:50.760
He said it to the prophet back then, and He's saying it to the watchman now.

00:48:50.760 --> 00:49:04.520
It's going to be like a light switch.

00:49:04.520 --> 00:49:13.640
Is there an urgency in you?

00:49:33.095 --> 00:49:33.343
You shall walk, run, and fly spiritually speaking.

00:49:36.300 --> 00:49:37.215
That deserves a Hallelujah!

00:49:39.005 --> 00:49:50.400
I'm going to sing in the middle of a storm.

00:49:55.428 --> 00:50:03.434
The Lord said there's not enough urgency in His body.

00:50:03.434 --> 00:50:18.040
Jesus is standing at the door with His hand on the doorknob, waiting on His Father's instructions.

00:50:18.707 --> 00:50:29.698
The Rapture of the church is at hand.

00:50:40.733 --> 00:50:44.760
I saw a vast field of wheat that was ripe and bending over.

00:50:44.760 --> 00:51:06.200
The Lord showed me glory stacks of farm equipment in a barn to bring in the harvest.

00:51:10.826 --> 00:51:23.920
My church does not have enough urgency behind the pulpits.

00:51:23.920 --> 00:51:46.116
Even the people you look up to on YouTube—He said there's not enough urgency even in them.

00:51:46.116 --> 00:51:59.460
He said they're focused on money and financial gains.

00:52:01.200 --> 00:52:13.727
The financial outpouring is to bring in the harvest with the net.

00:52:13.727 --> 00:52:32.766
It's a blessing, but the basis is to bring in the harvest so that none should perish.

00:52:32.766 --> 00:52:58.280
Just as a groom brings gifts for the bride in Jewish tradition, He's bringing these gifts.

00:52:58.280 --> 00:53:05.1000
Keep your eyes vertical, not horizontal.

00:53:05.1000 --> 00:53:13.995
All the wealth will be left here anyway.

00:53:13.995 --> 00:53:20.861
Seek Him, not His hand.

00:53:20.861 --> 00:53:41.446
You're only going to have that financial outpouring for a short time before the Rapture.

00:53:41.446 --> 00:53:57.149
It's just a transfer to fund the Gospel so we're not hindered.

00:53:57.149 --> 00:54:26.702
It's not time to buy a yacht or a Ferrari; it's about a transfer to go out of here like a rocket ship.

00:54:36.114 --> 00:54:40.739
The people in the Tribulation are going to need it.

00:54:40.739 --> 00:55:06.090
I've been there; I've seen it with Jesus—no food, no water.

00:55:06.090 --> 00:55:28.777
Two or three nights ago, the Lord showed me the black horse and the pale horse riding together.

00:55:28.777 --> 00:55:39.733
I saw the drought of weather manipulation.

00:55:39.733 --> 00:55:49.056
They are going to lose control of it.

00:55:49.056 --> 00:56:11.737
I saw mighty shakings coming with the weather because man is playing with something they don't understand.

00:56:13.355 --> 00:56:23.003
I saw drought coming for population control.

00:56:30.386 --> 00:56:39.085
The black horse will ride through Africa, Europe, and the Middle East.

00:56:39.085 --> 00:56:53.600
It left a black trail in the atmosphere.

00:56:53.600 --> 00:57:01.039
There will be plagues and pestilences.

00:57:01.039 --> 00:57:16.846
I saw peace and safety followed by sudden destruction.

00:57:24.990 --> 00:57:25.520
I saw escalation with Putin.

00:57:26.050 --> 00:57:47.079
The Lord told me not to say some things because they are designed to shake and awaken.

00:57:47.079 --> 00:58:12.640
75% of people watching may not have the urgency, but the 25 percenters sense something is coming.

00:58:12.640 --> 00:58:30.240
Others want to ignore it and call it fear-mongering.

00:58:40.513 --> 00:58:52.017
You couldn't stop COVID or 9/11; certain things are designed to awaken people.

00:58:52.017 --> 00:59:04.897
God allows things to take place because there's no urgency.

00:59:04.897 --> 00:59:17.535
It's a spanking to get people to wake up from their apathy.

00:59:17.535 --> 00:59:28.816
Lose sight of self and gain the Holy Ghost.

00:59:28.816 --> 00:59:32.709
Wake up every day with the expectation that God's going to do the supernatural through you.

00:59:32.709 --> 00:59:36.600
Like John G.

00:59:36.600 --> 00:59:49.580
Lake, see yourself as a carrier of the anointing.

00:59:49.580 --> 00:59:58.110
We have this treasure in earthen vessels.

00:59:58.110 --> 01:00:07.204
Diana is my intercessor, my praying mama.

01:00:07.204 --> 01:00:18.620
Let's take communion and believe for a miracle.

01:00:18.620 --> 01:00:31.960
We're trying to shake you because there's an urgency.

01:00:31.960 --> 01:00:40.794
Father, we want to be awake.

01:00:40.794 --> 01:01:04.300
We thank You that You were wounded for our transgressions and by Your stripes we are healed.

01:01:04.300 --> 01:01:19.400
Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

01:01:19.400 --> 01:01:36.480
We are redeemed from cancer, lack, diabetes, and all kinds of sickness.

01:01:43.497 --> 01:01:48.305
We take this in remembrance of what You did.

01:01:48.305 --> 01:02:01.453
We apply the blood of Jesus over our households and our minds.

01:02:01.453 --> 01:02:12.184
No weapon formed against us shall prosper.

01:02:12.184 --> 01:02:37.479
We say a thousand shall fall at our side, but it will not come near us.

01:02:55.280 --> 01:02:55.680
The blood of Jesus covers us.

01:03:02.263 --> 01:03:17.607
We confess our sins, and You are faithful to cleanse us.

01:03:17.607 --> 01:03:37.599
We take this communion every day because we are one with Him.

01:03:47.746 --> 01:03:51.479
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

01:03:52.609 --> 01:04:09.350
He is still healing the sick and casting out devils through us.

01:04:09.350 --> 01:04:21.929
Submit yourself to God, resist the devil, and he will flee.

01:04:21.929 --> 01:05:03.510
He's not going to do any more about the devil for you; He already did it.

01:05:03.520 --> 01:05:16.360
You must resist.

01:05:16.360 --> 01:06:30.760
If you have bad dreams or tears in your marriage, plead the blood of Jesus.

01:06:39.119 --> 01:07:17.589
Jesus is your attorney at the mercy seat, and Satan is the accuser.

01:07:34.800 --> 01:08:05.829
When you are asked how you plead, say 'I plead the blood.

01:08:05.839 --> 01:09:04.349
' His blood washes you white as snow and makes you innocent before the Father.

01:09:04.359 --> 01:09:45.328
He paid the price for you and me on Calvary's tree.

01:09:45.328 --> 01:10:17.208
Jesus is making intercession for you right now.

01:10:19.384 --> 01:10:53.528
The only way to stand against the devil is by the blood of the Lamb and the word of our testimony.

01:10:53.528 --> 01:11:09.834
None of us have enough good works; we all deserve hell, but it's by His blood we are free.

01:11:09.834 --> 01:11:16.792
Christ redeemed us from the curse.

01:11:17.980 --> 01:11:39.880
He became poor that we might be rich.

01:11:39.880 --> 01:11:56.960
Poverty is a spiritual leprosy.

01:12:12.430 --> 01:12:13.480
This communion is about relationship, not a religious act.

01:12:13.480 --> 01:12:19.617
Father, Your face is all I seek.

01:12:19.617 --> 01:12:29.257
[Music] Jesus, what a wonder You are.

01:12:38.800 --> 01:12:39.210
You shine like the bright morning star.

01:12:39.210 --> 01:12:47.097
Jesus, You're the sweetest name of all.

01:12:51.120 --> 01:12:54.261
You always hear me when I call.

01:12:56.575 --> 01:13:02.300
You lift me up each time I fall.

01:13:02.300 --> 01:13:12.680
I believe in miracles; I've seen a soul set free.

01:13:12.680 --> 01:13:21.440
Miraculous the change in one redeemed through Calvary.

01:13:21.440 --> 01:13:34.639
I've seen the lily push its way up through the stubborn sod.

01:13:34.639 --> 01:13:46.840
I believe in miracles, for I believe in God.

01:14:03.687 --> 01:14:03.943
I sang that the other day and the glory filled our car.

01:14:03.943 --> 01:14:13.800
A man started dancing in the road in front of us.

01:14:24.520 --> 01:14:24.693
I expect miracles every day.

01:14:30.788 --> 01:14:32.587
We pray this video blessed you.

01:14:32.587 --> 01:14:50.080
We'll never ask you for money; the Lord said to preach the Gospel freely.

01:14:54.719 --> 01:14:54.939
Don't fall for impersonators or scams.

01:15:02.310 --> 01:15:02.500
We don't do crypto investments.

01:15:02.500 --> 01:15:14.812
Subscribe and like to help the algorithm spread the Gospel.

01:15:15.216 --> 01:15:23.613
We have new channels for many countries.

01:15:23.613 --> 01:15:45.520
I'm believing the Iron Curtain will come down in North Korea and Kim Jong Un will be dealt with.

01:15:47.444 --> 01:16:00.520
We must pray for those who cannot hear about Jesus.

01:16:00.520 --> 01:16:09.205
Put a smile on your face; Jesus loves you.

01:16:09.205 --> 01:16:12.880
God bless you all.

01:16:12.880 --> 01:16:17.760
Bye-bye.
